<p><font face="Verdana" size="+1">Youth Ministry in the Diocese of Chicago seeks to:</font></p>
<UL type="disc">
<LI>To enhance Youth Ministry in the congregations of our Diocese,
providing resources, networking opportunities, and programming
that affirms the diversity of all persons, cultures, ideas, and
theology within our church.
<LI>Consultation in the development and continuation of parish
youth programs.
<LI>Leadership Training for  Adults and Youth for use in their
own congregations and beyond.
<LI>To serve as a key source of communication between local, diocesan,
provincial, and national Youth networks, parishes and individuals,
through:<br><br>

<ul type="circle">
<LI>General mailings to parishes, youth advisors, and youth.
<LI>The Youth Newsletter, &quot;God's Youth In Action&quot;
<LI>Sharing of youth ministry resources from the National Church.
<LI>Updating of the youth mailing list
<LI>Updating of adult contact names for Youth Ministry in the
parishes.
